          <heading>Minimum tax in combined return</heading>
          <content>
            <p>Sec. 12-223c. Minimum tax in combined return.Each corporation included in a combined return under section12-223ashall pay the minimum tax of two hundred fifty dollars prescribed under section12-219. No tax credit allowed against the tax imposed by this chapter shall reduce an included corporation's tax calculated under section12-219to an amount less than two hundred fifty dollars.
